[[iftags +визуальный_элемент]]
[[>]]
[[module Rate]]
[[/>]]

[[module CSS]]
code, .code, .code pre {
  background: #f7f7f7;
  color: #050;
  font-weight: 500;
  font-family: 'Cascadia Mono', 'Courier New', Courier, FreeMono, monospace;
}

code {
  padding: 4px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.code {
  padding: 8px;
}

.code p, .code pre {
  margin: 0;
}

.addendum-block {
  margin: 16px 0;
  border: 1px solid #dcdcdc;
  background: white;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 3px #ccc;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.addendum-title {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 4px 24px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  background: linear-gradient(to top, #d8d8d8, #ececec);
  border-bottom: 1px solid #dcdcdc;
}
.addendum-content {
  padding: 8px 24px;
}
[[/module]]

[[div class="addendum-block"]]
[[div_ class="addendum-title"]]
Описание визуального элемента
[[/div]]


[[div class="addendum-content"]]
**Описание:** Данный визуальный элемент является шаблоном плаката Цирка Германа Фуллера .

**Примеры в статьях:** [[[the-amazing-sluggo|Герман Фуллер представляет: Удивительный Слизневик ]]]

**Параметры:** 
* {{title}} -- Название плаката.

* {{textLeft}} --Текст слева от фото.

* {{image}} -- Ссылка на изображение.

* {{textRight}} -- Текст справа от фото.

* {{textBottom}} -- Текст снизу фото.

* {{textFooter}} -- Текст внизу плаката.

**Пример использования:**
> [[include component:hf-poster
> |title=Рыба
> |textLeft=Рыба
> |image=http://scpfoundation.ru/local--files/the-living-head/elisa.png
> |textRight=Рыба
> |textBottom=Рыба
> |textFooter=Рыба
> ]]

[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[/iftags]] 
[[iftags -визуальный_элемент]]
[[module CSS]]
@import url(/local--files/component:hf-poster/amerika-font.css);
[[/module]]

[[module css]]

.hfcontainer
{
    max-width: 707px !important;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    overflow: visible;
    padding: 0px 0px;
    border: collapse;
    background-image: url("http://files.scpfoundation.net/local--files/component:hf-poster/Herman-Fuller-background-r.png");
    background-size: 100% 100%;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    color: #BEB192;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px #000;
}

.hfheader
{
    padding: 0px 0px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    height: 80px;
    width: 100%;
    display: bock;
}

.hfnarrowcontent
{
    flex-grow: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    flex-basis: 20%;
    font-size: 2em;
    font-family: amerikaregular;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0% 2%;
    padding-bottom: 0px;
    margin: 0px 0px;
}

.hfnarrowcontent p
{
    line-height: 110%;
}

.hftitle
{
   font-size: 3.2em;
   font-family: amerikaregular;
   font-weight: bold;
   text-align: center;
   height: 75px;
   width: 100%;
   padding: 0px 0px;
   margin: 0px 0px;
   display: block;
}

.hfwidecontent
{
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    overflow: visible;
    font-size: 1.5em;
    font-family: amerikaregular;
    text-align: center;
    padding-bottom: -20px;
    margin: 0px 0px;
    margin-top: 30px;
}

.hfwidecontent p
{
    line-height: 120%;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding: 0px 15px 0px 15px;
}

.hffooter
{
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    overflow: visible;
    font-family: amerikaregular;
    padding: 0px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.8em;
}

.hfpic
{
    width: 30%;
    flex-grow: 0;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin: 0px 0px;
    padding: 0px 0px;
    background-position: center center;
    position: relative;
}

.hfpicframe
{
    background-image: url("https://files.scpfoundation.net/local--files/component:hf-poster/frame-new.png");
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center center;
    background-size: 100% 100%;
    margin: 0px 0px;
    padding: 0px 0px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 1;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
}

.hfpic-container
{
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0px 0px;
    padding: 0px 0px;
    display: flex;
    text-align: center;
    align-items: center;
}

.table
{
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    overflow: visible;
    padding: 0px 0px;
    margin: 0px 0px;
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 1000px) {
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        font-size: 18pt;
    }

    .hfwidecontent p{
        font-size: 0.8em;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 975px) {
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 3.1em;
       height: 60px;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 950px) {
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 2.5em;
       height: 50px;
    }
    .hfwidecontent{
        margin-top: 15px;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 890px) {
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        font-size: 15pt;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 830px) {
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 2.2em;
       height: 50px;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        font-size: 13pt;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent p{
        margin: 10px 0px 10px 0px;
    }
    .hfwidecontent p{
        font-size: 0.7em;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 767px) {
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 2.8em;
       height: 65px;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        font-size: 18pt;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent p{
        margin: 30px 0px 30px 0px;
    }
    .hfwidecontent p{
        font-size: 1.1em;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 715px) {
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 2.5em;
       height: 50px;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        width: 22%;
        font-size: 17pt;
    }
    .hfwidecontent{
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .hfwidecontent p{
        font-size: 0.9em;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 675px) {
    .hfpic {
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 625px) {
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 2.3em;
       height: 40px;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        width: 20%;
        font-size: 15pt;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent p{
        margin: 20px 0px 20px 0px;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 585px) {
    .hfheader {
    padding-top: 20px;
    height: 60px;
    }
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 2.1em;
       height: 25px;
    }
    .hfwidecontent{
        margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .hfwidecontent p{
        font-size: 0.8em;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 515px) {
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        width: 19%;
        font-size: 12pt;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent p{
        margin: 12px 0px 12px 0px;
    }
    .hfwidecontent{
        margin-top: 0px;
    }
    .hfwidecontent p{
        font-size: 0.7em;
    }
}
@media only screen and (max-width: 460px) {
    .hfheader {
    padding-top: 20px;
    height: 40px;
    }
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 2.1em;
       height: 25px;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        width: 19%;
        font-size: 10pt;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent p{
        margin: 12px 0px 12px 0px;
    }
    .hfwidecontent p{
        font-size: 0.6em;
    }
}

[[/module]]

@@ @@
[[div class="hfcontainer"]]
[[div_ class="table"]]
    [[div_ class="hfheader"]]
     @@ @@
    [[/div]]
    [[div class="hftitle"]]
     {$title}
    [[/div]]
    [[div_ class="hfpic-container"]]
    [[div class="hfnarrowcontent"]]
     {$textLeft}
    [[/div]]\
        [[div_ class="hfpic"]]
            [[image {$image}]]
            [[div_ class="hfpicframe"]]
            @@ @@
            [[/div]]
        [[/div]]\
    [[div class="hfnarrowcontent"]]
     {$textRight}
    [[/div]]
    [[/div]]
    [[div class="hfwidecontent"]]
     {$textBottom}
    [[/div]]
    [[div_ class="hffooter"]]
     {$textFooter}
    [[/div]]
 [[/div]]
[[/div]] 
[[/iftags]]
